<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'changelog' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="page" id="main-content" role="main">
<section class="lp-section">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:680px;">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="eyebrow">changelog</div>
      <h2>what's new at perch.</h2>
      <p>every update, improvement, and fix. we ship continuously — this page tracks everything that lands.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cl-list">
      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">major</div>
        <h3>app parser 2.0</h3>
        <p>expanded to 50+ uk providers across insurance, broadband, domains, saas, streaming, and gyms. bulk paste mode — paste multiple emails separated by "---" to parse them all at once. 3-step onboarding flow for new visitors with sample email. smart insights panel shows biggest overpayment, upcoming renewals, and total potential savings after each item added. contract length and cancellation window detection.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>6 new blog articles</h3>
        <p>gym contract traps, mobile upgrade costs, streaming service creep, pet insurance loyalty penalty, travel insurance auto-renewal, and landlord insurance chaos. blog now has 11 articles total.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>real email capture on all forms</h3>
        <p>footer, blog, and newsletter-cta subscribe forms now POST to the live waitlist api. real success/error states, deduplication detection, and source tracking per form.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>social proof engine</h3>
        <p>testimonials auto-rotate every 8 seconds with crossfade and navigation dots. pause on scroll-out, resume on scroll-in. savings ticker shows live potential savings calculated from waitlist data. css variable-based inline critical styles so light mode works correctly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>nav &amp; layout polish</h3>
        <p>desktop nav trimmed to 6 essential links. drawer nav reorganized with primary/secondary divider. footer links reduced to 13. css cache version updated to break stale immutable cache.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>features page</h3>
        <p>new /features page catalogues every capability: email parser, document extraction, verdict engine, weekly digest, price history, savings dash, vendor tracking, market benchmarking, calendar view, team forwarding, multi-inbox, and deadline alerts. each feature card shows supported formats and key stats.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>dashboard page</h3>
        <p>protected /dashboard showing a live mock of your perch. dashboard: stats cards (emails processed, savings found, renewing, needs action), upcoming renewals timeline with verdict badges, monthly savings bar chart, recent activity feed, and connected inboxes panel. password-gated with demo pass: perchdemo.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>blog: july renewal season</h3>
        <p>new article on why july is the peak month for auto-renewals across car insurance, broadband, gym memberships, and subscriptions. includes a 10-minute audit checklist and perch. integration notes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">4 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>demo page rebuilt for progressive enhancement</h3>
        <p>all 6 inbox items are now pre-rendered as html with fallback visibility. localStorage access is wrapped in robust try-catch blocks. the scanning overlay starts hidden and is only shown by js on first visit. demo works even when javascript is disabled or crashes — items are visible, formatted, and interactive by default.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">3 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>cost explorer tool</h3>
        <p>select your providers and see exactly what the loyalty penalty is costing you. live calculation with provider-specific overpayment rates for insurance, broadband, subscriptions, and domains.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">3 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>interactive product demo</h3>
        <p>watch perch. extract renewal data from forwarded emails in real-time. the demo simulates the full flow — forward, extract, verdict, digest — without needing an account.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">3 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>stats dashboard</h3>
        <p>live waitlist analytics at /stats. see signup totals, segment split, daily signup chart, and referral metrics in real-time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">3 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>multi-step onboarding</h3>
        <p>the waitlist signup flow is now a guided 3-step process: segment selection, cost calculator, and details. each step transitions smoothly, reducing friction and making the experience feel more intentional.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">3 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>pricing toggle (monthly / annual)</h3>
        <p>toggle between monthly and annual pricing on the /pricing page. annual pricing saves ~30% and updates in real-time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">2 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>blog improvements</h3>
        <p>added reading progress bar, breadcrumb navigation, related articles at the bottom of each post, article share button, and email subscribe form on the blog listing page.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">2 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>visual polish pass</h3>
        <p>custom inter fonts, full type scale and spacing grid, hamburger menu with slide-in overlay, 404 page in brand voice, custom scrollbar, focus-visible rings, and comprehensive mobile responsive across all pages.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">2 jul 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-improved">improved</div>
        <h3>landing page rewrite</h3>
        <p>10-section landing page with 3d css hero scene, glassmorphism panels, card tilt on hover, scroll progress bar, floating amber orbs, and particle system.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">30 jun 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>blog engine</h3>
        <p>article listing, detail pages with dynamic includes, rss feed, and 5 articles covering the loyalty penalty, car insurance, broadband pricing, subscription traps, and domain lapses.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">28 jun 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>waitlist dashboard &amp; referral system</h3>
        <p>email-based dashboard showing queue position, referral code with tracking, estimated access date, and a 4-stage timeline. referral system moves you up the queue.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">25 jun 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>cost calculator on waitlist page</h3>
        <p>four sliders (insurance, subscriptions, broadband, domains) calculate your estimated annual overpayment based on uk average rates. the total is submitted with the signup.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">20 jun 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>brand identity system</h3>
        <p>svg wordmark, favicon, og image, and a brand guide page with voice principles, colour swatches, copy patterns, and a "never say" list.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cl-entry">
        <div class="cl-date">18 jun 2026</div>
        <div class="cl-badge cl-badge-new">new</div>
        <h3>full multi-page site launch</h3>
        <p>express/ejs architecture with 11 pages, vercel deployment, waitlist api, and the complete perch. brand. pages: index, problem, how-it-works, comparison, proof, pricing, uses, waitlist, privacy, brand, dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>